\[\begin{split} \frac{1}{n^2h} Ek\left(\frac{X_i-x}{h}\right)^2=&\frac{1}{n^2h}\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}k\left(\frac{z-x}{h}\right)^2f(z)dz\\ =&\frac{1}{nh}\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}k(u)^2f(x+hu)du\\ =&\frac{1}{nh}\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}k(u)^2(f(x)+O(h))du\\ =&\frac{\left(f(x)+O(h)\right)R(k)}{nh} \end{split}\] \(R(k)=\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}k(u)^2du\)

library(KernSmooth);
## KernSmooth 2.23 loaded
## Copyright M. P. Wand 1997-2009
#  
density <- bkde(faithful$eruptions)

# 
plot(density,type = 'l', col = 'blue', lwd = 2, 
     main = 'Kernel Density Estimate', 
     xlab = 'Sepal Length', ylab = 'Density', 
     xlim = range(faithful$eruptions),
     ylim = c(0, max(density$y) * 1.2))

R
Silverman \(h = 1.06\hat{\sigma} n^{-1/5}\) \(\hat{\sigma}\) \(n\)
\[\frac{1}{\sqrt{2\pi}h}\exp\left(-\frac{(x - x_i)^2}{2h^2}\right)\] \(x_i\)\(x\)\(h\)


# 
data <- rnorm(100, mean = 10, sd = 2)

# 
h <- 1.06 * sd(data) * length(data)^(-1/5)

# 
x <- seq(min(data), max(data), length.out = 1000)

# 
dens <- rep(0, length(x))
for (i in seq_along(dens)) {
  for (j in seq_along(data)) {
    dens[i] <- dens[i] + dnorm(x[i], mean = data[j], sd = h)
  }
}

# 
density <- dens / (length(data) * h)

# 
plot(x, density, type = "l")
